<i>A wedge driven into the
wasteland of my memory</i>

2138
02:28:25,576 --> 02:28:29,523
<i>At dawn, a blood-red sun
rose over the Atlantic Ocean</i>

2139
02:28:29,523 --> 02:28:33,470
Old man!

2140
02:28:33,470 --> 02:28:37,417
Don’t come any closer!

2141
02:28:37,417 --> 02:28:41,364
Damn it...

2142
02:28:41,364 --> 02:28:45,311
Fucking hell!

2143
02:28:45,311 --> 02:28:49,258
<i>There’s nothing I can do,
I’m a mere spectator</i>

2144
02:28:49,258 --> 02:28:53,205
<i>I’ve got nothing, I’m powerless</i>

2145
02:28:53,205 --> 02:28:57,152
<i>Come on, get real,
even at a time like this?</i>

2146
02:28:57,152 --> 02:29:01,099
<i>Even if I give up, the pain
will just be for another day</i>

2147
02:29:01,099 --> 02:29:05,046
<i>And tomorrow, yes tomorrow,</i>

2148
02:29:05,046 --> 02:29:09,000
<i>I’ll still be over here crying like a loser</i>

2149
02:29:09,000 --> 02:29:11,000
Honourable knight,

2150
02:29:11,000 --> 02:29:15,611
Is revenge your answer?

2151
02:29:15,611 --> 02:29:20,222
Is that what you take pride in?

2152
02:29:20,222 --> 02:29:24,833
If you want to preach, then fight
with your pride on the line!

2153
02:29:24,833 --> 02:29:29,444
You can lecture me after you win!

2154
02:29:29,444 --> 02:29:34,055
<i>Now’s the time, to let
courage resonate in my heart</i>

2155
02:29:34,055 --> 02:29:38,666
<i>I’m not scared of pain</i>

2156
02:29:38,666 --> 02:29:43,277
<i>I must find the strength to stand up</i>

2157
02:29:43,277 --> 02:29:47,888
<i>Tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow,</i>

2158
02:29:47,888 --> 02:29:52,499
<i>Tomorrow is right now!</i>

2159
02:29:52,499 --> 02:29:57,110
Old man!

2160
02:29:57,110 --> 02:30:01,721
Melt!

2161
02:30:01,721 --> 02:30:06,332
I didn’t follow you to
become a hindrance!

2162
02:30:06,332 --> 02:30:10,943
Speedwagon...

2163
02:30:10,943 --> 02:30:15,554
<i>I’ll let courage resonate in my heart</i>

2164
02:30:15,554 --> 02:30:20,165
<i>And look the enemy in the eyes</i>

2165
02:30:20,165 --> 02:30:24,776
<i>Won’t wait for a distant tomorrow</i>

2166
02:30:24,776 --> 02:30:29,387
<i>I’ll start walking,</i>
{\ O (spread): It's the story of a proud knight.}

2167
02:30:29,387 --> 02:30:33,998
<i>Find the strength to
get back on my feet</i>

2168
02:30:33,998 --> 02:30:38,609
<i>Tomorrow is now!</i>

2169
02:30:38,609 --> 02:30:43,220
JoJo!

2170
02:30:43,220 --> 02:30:47,831
Cut finely, beat of my blood!

2171
02:30:47,831 --> 02:30:52,442
Please... This knight’s proud heart,

2172
02:30:52,442 --> 02:30:57,060
Let it somehow be restored!

2173
02:30:57,060 --> 02:30:59,060
I am the Dark Knight Bruford!

2174
02:30:59,060 --> 02:31:03,691
This pain means nothing to me!

2175
02:31:03,691 --> 02:31:08,322
Why aren’t you moving?

2176
02:31:08,322 --> 02:31:12,953
Just now,

2177
02:31:12,953 --> 02:31:17,584
You said “pain”.

2178
02:31:17,584 --> 02:31:22,215
That means that now,

2179
02:31:22,215 --> 02:31:26,846
You can feel pain!

2180
02:31:26,846 --> 02:31:31,477
Pain?

2181
02:31:31,477 --> 02:31:36,108
That’s why...

2182
02:31:36,108 --> 02:31:40,739
I stopped fighting you.

2183
02:31:40,739 --> 02:31:45,370
That’s why you stopped your sword.

2184
02:31:45,370 --> 02:31:50,001
You are a great knight.

2185
02:31:50,001 --> 02:31:54,632
You are human!

2186
02:31:54,632 --> 02:31:59,263
Pain...

2187
02:31:59,263 --> 02:32:03,894
Is proof of life!

2188
02:32:03,894 --> 02:32:08,525
So this is what it means to be human?
{\ O (spread): I trained that strength}

2189
02:32:08,525 --> 02:32:13,156
Because of this pain, I can also feel
the joy of being alive in this moment.

2190
02:32:13,156 --> 02:32:17,787
I feel a bizarre sense of peace now.

2191
02:32:17,787 --> 02:32:22,418
Bruford...

2192
02:32:22,418 --> 02:32:27,060
I dedicate to you the word
engraved in my sword.

2193
02:32:27,060 --> 02:32:29,060
Luck!

2194
02:32:29,060 --> 02:32:29,060
And also...

2195
02:32:29,060 --> 02:32:31,060
Pluck!

2196
02:32:31,060 --> 02:32:35,060
To think, I had to kill him
in order to save his soul...

2197
02:32:35,060 --> 02:32:39,060
Damn you!

2198
02:32:39,060 --> 02:32:43,060
JoJo!

2199
02:32:43,060 --> 02:32:47,060
I can’t believe you actually
defeated the Dark Knight!

2200
02:32:47,060 --> 02:32:51,060
Just as I thought...

2201
02:32:51,060 --> 02:32:55,060
I, Dio, will—

2202
02:32:55,060 --> 02:32:59,060
Hey baby!

2203
02:32:59,060 --> 02:33:03,060
I bet the blow from that
ripple-charged flower must hurt!
{\ O (spread): There's no way we could refuse}

2204
02:33:03,060 --> 02:33:05,060
What the...

2205
02:33:05,060 --> 02:33:15,726
Your ripple is more vulgar than frog piss!

2206
02:33:15,726 --> 02:33:26,392
Watch out, Mr. Joestar!

2207
02:33:26,392 --> 02:33:37,058
What an embarrassment of a knight!

2208
02:33:37,058 --> 02:33:47,724
He never got his revenge!
{\ O (spread): Your master is not imprisoned.}

2209
02:33:47,724 --> 02:33:58,390
What did he have to be joyful about!

2210
02:33:58,390 --> 02:34:09,060
JoJo!

2211
02:34:09,060 --> 02:34:11,060
No!

2212
02:34:11,060 --> 02:34:17,417
How could you!

2213
02:34:17,417 --> 02:34:23,774
For victory!

2214
02:34:23,774 --> 02:34:30,131
I take pride in victory!

2215
02:34:30,131 --> 02:34:36,488
Fuck!

2216
02:34:36,488 --> 02:34:42,845
I’ll get you!

2217
02:34:42,845 --> 02:34:49,202
I’ll get you for this!

2218
02:34:49,202 --> 02:34:55,559
JoJo...

2219
02:34:55,559 --> 02:35:01,916
JoJo!

2220
02:35:01,916 --> 02:35:08,273
My final ripple...

2221
02:35:08,273 --> 02:35:14,630
My... dying wish is...

2222
02:35:14,630 --> 02:35:20,987
That you take my ripple
and continue on, JoJo!

2223
02:35:20,987 --> 02:35:27,344
He collapsed.

2224
02:35:27,344 --> 02:35:33,701
I’ll vanquish your wicked soul!

2225
02:35:33,701 --> 02:35:40,058
Drown in the murk of history, Tarkus!

2226
02:35:40,058 --> 02:35:46,415
Old man!

2227
02:35:46,415 --> 02:35:52,772
Mr. Zeppeli!
{\ O (spread): You may be right.}

2228
02:35:52,772 --> 02:35:59,129
If we lose you—

2229
02:35:59,129 --> 02:36:05,486
There’s no time to be sad.

2230
02:36:05,486 --> 02:36:11,843
The Stone Mask must be destroyed!

2231
02:36:11,843 --> 02:36:18,200
Old man!

2232
02:36:18,200 --> 02:36:24,557
I...

2233
02:36:24,557 --> 02:36:30,914
I lived my own life to the fullest.

2234
02:36:30,914 --> 02:36:37,271
In the end,

2235
02:36:37,271 --> 02:36:43,628
I leave everything I have to you.

2236
02:36:43,628 --> 02:36:50,000
JoJo,

2237
02:36:50,000 --> 02:36:53,000
You are my hope.

2238
02:40:00,000 --> 02:40:08,000
<i>Once again, life is
spilling out of my arms</i>

2239
02:40:08,000 --> 02:40:14,500
<i>You showed me my purpose</i>

2240
02:40:14,500 --> 02:40:21,000
<i>Who I am meant to be</i>

2241
02:40:21,000 --> 02:40:32,000
<i>You taught me that humanity’s
greatest gift is courage</i>

2242
02:40:32,000 --> 02:40:36,000
<i>The light you’ve given
to me will shine through</i>

2243
02:40:36,000 --> 02:40:40,000
<i>Into my spirit</i>

2244
02:40:40,000 --> 02:40:44,000
It felt like...

2245
02:40:44,000 --> 02:40:52,000
I had a friend and a son
in you at the same time.

2246
02:40:52,000 --> 02:40:52,352
From here on...

2247
02:40:52,352 --> 02:40:52,704
I live within you.

2248
02:40:52,704 --> 02:40:53,056
JoJo.

2249
02:40:53,056 --> 02:40:53,408
<i>Everything is connected</i>

2250
02:40:53,408 --> 02:40:53,760
<i>There’s a meaning to it all</i>

2251
02:40:53,760 --> 02:40:54,112
<i>That’s what I’ve come to believe</i>

2252
02:40:54,112 --> 02:40:54,464
<i>Even this pain...</i>

2253
02:40:54,464 --> 02:40:54,816
<i>Even this pain</i>

2254
02:40:54,816 --> 02:40:55,168
<i>My father left to me
what you leave to me now</i>

2255
02:40:55,168 --> 02:40:55,520
<i>The golden light that
shines from within me</i>

2256
02:40:55,520 --> 02:40:55,872
<i>It’s the one thing in my heart
that I can hold on to now</i>

2257
02:40:55,872 --> 02:40:56,224
<i>I embrace it tightly</i>

2258
02:40:56,224 --> 02:40:56,576
<i>And from this prison...</i>

2259
02:40:56,576 --> 02:40:56,928
<i>I see the stars</i>

2260
02:40:56,928 --> 02:40:57,280
<i>A golden spirit</i>
{\ O (spread): Pride, the great wrestler Bruford}

2261
02:40:57,280 --> 02:40:57,632
<i>Humanity’s glow in the darkness</i>

2262
02:40:57,632 --> 02:40:58,000
<i>Will light up</i>

2263
02:40:58,000 --> 02:41:00,000
<i>The way to you...</i>

2264
02:41:00,000 --> 02:42:34,000
Dio!

2265
02:42:34,000 --> 02:42:43,000
<i>Light up the way to you...</i>

2266
02:42:43,000 --> 02:43:00,000
JoJo...!

2267
02:43:00,000 --> 02:43:17,000
<i>Dio...</i>

2268
02:43:17,000 --> 02:43:34,000
<i>Dio...</i>

2269
02:43:34,000 --> 02:43:41,000
<i>Can’t you hear my voice?</i>

2270
02:43:41,000 --> 02:43:41,333
<i>The voice calling for you?</i>

2271
02:43:41,333 --> 02:43:41,666
<i>I can’t hear you</i>

2272
02:43:41,666 --> 02:43:42,000
{\an8}<i>Dio...</i>

2273
02:43:42,000 --> 02:43:50,000
<i>I already killed my past</i>

2274
02:43:50,000 --> 02:43:51,000
{\an8}<i>Dio...</i>

2275
02:43:51,000 --> 02:43:59,000
<i>Don’t call my name—</i>

2276
02:43:59,000 --> 02:44:02,607
<i>You and I are different</i>

2277
02:44:02,607 --> 02:44:06,214
<i>We’re not so different, you’re my son</i>

2278
02:44:06,214 --> 02:44:09,821
<i>I have changed into something new</i>

2279
02:44:09,821 --> 02:44:13,428
<i>You’re not so changed,
you did it to survive</i>

2280
02:44:13,428 --> 02:44:17,035
<i>I’ll use any means</i>

2281
02:44:17,035 --> 02:44:20,642
<i>DIO: I’ll steal it all
DARIO: You’ll steal it all</i>

2282
02:44:20,642 --> 02:44:24,249
<i>DIO: Upend righteousness</i>

2283
02:44:24,249 --> 02:44:27,856
<i>DARIO: You’re my clever boy!</i>

2284
02:44:27,856 --> 02:44:31,463
<i>DIO: I will conquer it all</i>

2285
02:44:31,463 --> 02:44:35,070
<i>DARIO: What will you want next?</i>

2286
02:44:35,070 --> 02:44:38,677
<i>DIO: I will dominate everything</i>

2287
02:44:38,677 --> 02:44:42,284
<i>Go ahead and dominate,
what will you want after that?</i>

2288
02:44:42,284 --> 02:44:45,891
<i>What do I want?</i>

2289
02:44:45,891 --> 02:44:49,498
<i>DARIO: What do you want?</i>

2290
02:44:49,498 --> 02:44:53,105
<i>DIO: What do I want?</i>

2291
02:44:53,105 --> 02:44:56,712
<i>I want...</i>
{\ O (spread): Fuck}

2292
02:44:56,712 --> 02:45:00,319
<i>I want...</i>
{\ O (spread): Fuck}

2293
02:45:00,319 --> 02:45:03,926
{\an8}<i>Dio... Dio...</i>

2294
02:45:03,926 --> 02:45:07,533
<i>I want...</i>

2295
02:45:07,533 --> 02:45:11,140
So you’ve come...

2296
02:45:11,140 --> 02:45:14,747
JoJo.

2297
02:45:14,747 --> 02:45:18,354
Is this...

2298
02:45:18,354 --> 02:45:21,961
The world you wished for?

2299
02:45:21,961 --> 02:45:25,568
What?

2300
02:45:25,568 --> 02:45:29,175
The world...

2301
02:45:29,175 --> 02:45:32,782
That you’ve been trying
to obtain for so long...

2302
02:45:32,782 --> 02:45:36,389
Surrounded by death...

2303
02:45:36,389 --> 02:45:40,000
It’s a pitiful world, isn’t it?

2304
02:45:40,000 --> 02:45:50,000
It’s a splendid world where
I’ve dominated everything.

2305
02:45:50,000 --> 02:45:54,000
I’ve dominated death, and even history too.

2306
02:45:54,000 --> 02:45:58,000
For that reason, you stole
from uninvolved innocents?

2307
02:45:58,000 --> 02:46:03,000
They were a noble sacrifice for
the sake of the future that I designed.

2308
02:46:03,000 --> 02:46:07,400
You’re just afraid.

2309
02:46:07,400 --> 02:46:11,800
Of being human...
{\ O (spread): What if}

2310
02:46:11,800 --> 02:46:16,200
That’s why you rejected your humanity.

2311
02:46:16,200 --> 02:46:20,600
For the sake of obtaining this world...

2312
02:46:20,600 --> 02:46:25,000
I’ve <i>transcended</i> humanity!

2313
02:46:25,000 --> 02:46:27,000
You ran away from it.

2314
02:46:27,000 --> 02:46:31,700
The ends justify the means.

2315
02:46:31,700 --> 02:46:36,400
I will win,

2316
02:46:36,400 --> 02:46:41,100
And that means conquering
everything, of course.

2317
02:46:41,100 --> 02:46:45,800
All of this is fate!

2318
02:46:45,800 --> 02:46:50,500
No!

2319
02:46:50,500 --> 02:46:55,200
This is just how you
chose to live your life!

2320
02:46:55,200 --> 02:46:59,900
Opposing fate...

2321
02:46:59,900 --> 02:47:04,600
What will your legacy be?

2322
02:47:04,600 --> 02:47:09,300
Such righteousness!

2323
02:47:09,300 --> 02:47:14,000
Just like the one who gave me this power...

2324
02:47:14,000 --> 02:47:27,000
And then died!

2325
02:47:27,000 --> 02:47:27,000
Just like...

2326
02:47:27,000 --> 02:47:39,000
Your father.

2327
02:47:45,000 --> 02:47:47,000
That’s right.

2328
02:47:47,000 --> 02:48:01,000
As a gentleman, it pains
me to say this, but...

2329
02:48:01,000 --> 02:48:03,000
Now I, Jonathan Joestar...

2330
02:48:05,000 --> 02:48:07,000
For the sake of revenge...

2331
02:48:07,000 --> 02:48:09,000
Dio...

2332
02:48:09,000 --> 02:48:11,000
I will kill you!

2333
02:48:11,000 --> 02:48:13,666
We’re one and the same; you want
to exact your revenge! I admire that!

2334
02:48:13,666 --> 02:48:16,332
No! I’ve come to right your wrongs!
{\ O (spread): now}

2335
02:48:16,332 --> 02:48:19,000
I’ve accepted this as my legacy!

2336
02:48:19,000 --> 02:48:21,000
Speedwagon!

2337
02:48:21,000 --> 02:48:21,173
Right!

2338
02:48:21,173 --> 02:48:21,346
<i>Ironic, isn’t it? Now
you’re the have-not, JoJo!</i>

2339
02:48:21,346 --> 02:48:21,519
<i>I’ll suck you dry</i>

2340
02:48:21,519 --> 02:48:21,692
<i>Become my next meal!</i>

2341
02:48:21,692 --> 02:48:21,865
<i>I’ve lost so many loved ones but
their light lives on in me, Dio!</i>

2342
02:48:21,865 --> 02:48:22,038
<i>I’ve come to cleanse
your corrupted ambitions</i>

2343
02:48:22,038 --> 02:48:22,211
<i>Useless, useless, useless, useless!</i>

2344
02:48:22,211 --> 02:48:22,384
<i>I obtained this power</i>

2345
02:48:22,384 --> 02:48:22,557
<i>My heart’s aflame</i>

2346
02:48:22,557 --> 02:48:22,730
<i>So I could steal everything from you</i>

2347
02:48:22,730 --> 02:48:22,903
<i>I’ll dull this pain</i>

2348
02:48:22,903 --> 02:48:23,076
<i>If you think about it, you’re just like me</i>

2349
02:48:23,076 --> 02:48:23,249
<i>You were just like me,
two sides of the same coin</i>

2350
02:48:23,249 --> 02:48:23,422
<i>Like fire and ice, my body is burning</i>

2351
02:48:23,422 --> 02:48:23,595
<i>JOJO: I’ll kill you
DIO: You’ll kill me</i>

2352
02:48:23,595 --> 02:48:23,768
<i>JOJO: You’ll kill me
DIO: I’ll kill you</i>

2353
02:48:23,768 --> 02:48:23,941
Just like Mr. Zeppeli taught me!

2354
02:48:23,941 --> 02:48:24,114
I’ll channel my ripple through this sword!

2355
02:48:24,114 --> 02:48:24,287
You did it! You defeated Dio!

2356
02:48:24,287 --> 02:48:24,460
Not a chance!

2357
02:48:24,460 --> 02:48:24,633
You fools!

2358
02:48:24,633 --> 02:48:24,806
What! The sword is freezing—

2359
02:48:24,806 --> 02:48:25,000
Utterly pathetic!

2360
02:48:25,000 --> 02:48:27,000
Mr. Joestar!

2361
02:48:27,000 --> 02:48:50,250
JoJo!

2362
02:48:50,250 --> 02:49:13,500
<i>Utterly pathetic! I’m grasping
your carotid artery, JoJo!</i>

2363
02:49:13,500 --> 02:49:36,750
<i>With this, you’ll become
one of my undead servants</i>

2364
02:49:36,750 --> 02:50:00,000
<i>Ironic, isn’t it, Dio?</i>

2365
02:50:00,000 --> 02:50:07,000
<i>Just as I thought, you were
running away from humanity</i>

2366
02:50:07,000 --> 02:50:13,000
<i>Why don’t you freeze me now, Dio!</i>

2367
02:50:13,000 --> 02:50:13,142
My fist... Just from hitting him!

2368
02:50:13,142 --> 02:50:13,284
I transcended humanity!
None of you are on my level.

2369
02:50:13,284 --> 02:50:13,426
<i>You’re nothing but a monkey, JoJo!</i>

2370
02:50:13,426 --> 02:50:13,568
<i>JOJO: No, for as long as I have faith,
DIO: Compared to me, Dio!</i>
{\ O (spread): You are this Dio}

2371
02:50:13,568 --> 02:50:13,710
<i>DIO: Let’s test your willpower
JOJO: I will reach you!</i>

2372
02:50:13,710 --> 02:50:13,852
<i>As long as we have faith, we can grow</i>

2373
02:50:13,852 --> 02:50:13,994
<i>JOJO: Us humans...
DIO: To be human is to have limits</i>

2374
02:50:13,994 --> 02:50:14,136
<i>JOJO: That’s what he taught me
DIO: You can’t reach me!</i>

2375
02:50:14,136 --> 02:50:14,278
<i>Like fire and ice</i>

2376
